A '''fusion generator supply tank''' was a device for power generation and storage. Using standard fusion technology, it generally provided [[Starship/Legends|starships]] with energy for [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] travel.

==History==
It was often used on harsh [[Planet/Legends|worlds]] like [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. The [[Lars family/Legends|Lars family]] had a number of these at [[Lars homestead/Legends|their homestead]]. The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] also had various generators installed at many of their facilities to provide energy for the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Starfleet]] to allow their vessels the ability to do sub-light and hyperspace jumps.

